high_descs: Turn right, move to the round table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right, move to in front of the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Turn left, move to in front of the stove.
Put the knife in the pan on the left of the stove.
Turn right, move to in front of the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn left, move to in front of the stove.
Put the potato slice into the pan containing the knife.
Pick up the pan, containing the knife and potato slice, from the stove.
Turn right, move to the round table.
Put the pan on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with sliced potato on the round table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the black table.
Pick up the knife off of the table.
Turn around and head for the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink.
Turn left and go to the stove.
Put the knife in the pot on the left side of the stove.
Turn right and go back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn left and go back to the stove.
Put the potato in the left pot on the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left.
Turn around, go across the room, turn left and head to the table.
Put the pan on the table behind the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a slice of potato and a knife on the table.

high_descs: Go to the round black table
Pick up a knife
Go to the sink
Cut the potato in the sink
Go to the stove
Put the knife in the pot
Go to the sink
Take a potato slice
Go to the stove
Put the potato in the pot
Take the pot
Go to the round black table
Put the pot down on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a potato slice and knife down on a table
